description: A tasty dinner made in minutes. Save time on prep with this brilliant chicken meal the whole family will love.
keywords: Skewer & kebab,Low saturated fat,Low salt,Low sugar,Microwave,High protein,High fibre,Rice,Kale,Quick & easy lunch,Chicken,Dinner Made Easy
name: 15-Minute Chicken Kebabs Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 420g Macro organic black beans no added salt (drained)
375g RSPCA approved lemon and garlic chicken kebabs

recipeInstructions.text: Heat olive oil in a large frying pan over medium-high heat. Cook skewers, stirring occasionally, for 7-8 minutes or until cooked through. Remove from the heat.
Vent the microwave rice packet and microwave for 21/2 minutes. Add rice and black beans to the pan and stir to combine. Season well with salt and pepper.
Place salad ingredients and dressing from the kit in a medium bowl and toss to combine. Divide skewers and black bean rice and salad between plates to serve.
